name: Rhino Palatine Sigil
description: Pay homage to warriors of a more chivalrous time with this sigil.

languages.description: Erweise den Kriegern einer ritterlicheren Zeit die Ehre, mit diesem Siegel.
languages.name: Siegel: Rhino Palatine

languages.description: Rendez hommage aux guerriers d'un temps plus chevaleresque grâce à ce Sceau.
languages.name: Sceau Rhino Palatine

languages.description: Rendi omaggio ai guerrieri dei tempi cavallereschi con questo sigillo.
languages.name: Sigillo Rhino Palatine

languages.description: 이 시질로 중세 시대의 전사에게 경의를 표하세요.
languages.name: 라이노 팔라틴 시질

languages.description: Con este sello rinde homenaje a los guerreros de tiempos más caballerescos.
languages.name: Sello de Rhino Palatino

languages.description: 用这个纹章来向更具骑士精神时期的战士们致敬。
languages.name: Rhino 伯爵纹章

languages.description: Отдайте честь воинам древних времен с этим сигилом.
languages.name: Сигил: Рино Палатин

languages.description: このシジルを伴い、多くの騎士道時代の戦士に敬意を払おう。
languages.name: Rhino Palatine シジル

languages.description: Oddaj hołd wojownikom bardziej rycerskich czasów za pomocą tego znaku.
languages.name: Znak Rhino Palatine

languages.description: Com este brasão você presta homenagem aos guerreiros de uma era muito mais selvagem.
languages.name: Brasão: Rhino Palatine

languages.description: 用這個紋章來向更俠義時期的戰士們致敬。
languages.name: Rhino 伯爵紋章

languages.description: แสดงความเคารพต่อนักรบแห่งยุคอัศวินด้วยเครื่องหมายนี้
languages.name: เครื่องหมาย: Rhino Palatine

languages.description: Daha kültürlü bir zamanın savaşçılarına bu glif ile saygı göster.
languages.name: Rhino Palatine Mührü
